PrecisAuthorization for the two trips to QUÉBEC undertaken by GEORGES FARRAH, M.P. (Bonaventure--Gaspé--Îles-de-la-Madeleine--Pabok), from October 18 to October 21, 2001, and from November 7 to November 8, 2001, in order to meet with officials of the Alliance des pêcheurs professionnels du Québec, the Association québecoise de l'industrie de la pêche and with the Official Opposition critic for fisheries at the National Assembly of Quebec.
